# Backend Rules (Supabase + FastAPI)

## Stack
- **Supabase** — PostgreSQL, Auth (JWT), RLS, Storage, Realtime
- **FastAPI** — business logic (`backend/app/`)
- **Next.js** — frontend; `api.*` client → FastAPI

## Architecture
```
Next.js → Supabase Auth (login/register/session)
Next.js → FastAPI /api/v1/* (Bearer JWT)
FastAPI → Supabase PostgreSQL (service_role + RPC)
```

## Conventions
- Routers: `backend/app/routers/`
- Services: `backend/app/*_service.py`
- Auth: `deps.require_user_auth`
- Financial writes: service_role + RPC only — never client UPDATE on orders/ledger

## Frontend imports
- Supabase (auth/storage/realtime): `@/infrastructure/supabase/client`
- Business API: `@/infrastructure/api/client`

## Migrations
`supabase/migrations/` — apply with `pnpm db:push`

## Security
- Service role key backend only
- Never commit `.env`
- Document endpoints in `docs/API_REFERENCE.md`

Skill: `skills/ishbor-backend/SKILL.md`
